      "title": "Welcome to Overlay",
      "description": "Overlay is a full-stack AI workspace built with Next.js 15 and Convex. It provides multi-model AI chat, voice transcription, knowledge search, note-taking, media generation, and hosted computer sessions — all in one app. This tour walks you through the key areas of the codebase.",
